# venvpp2
Welcome to venvpp2!

This project is an evolution from previous venvpp.
The main enhancements with respect to its predecessor are:
*Conan v2* and *CMake v4* with the usage of CMakePresets as first class citizens replacing the older custom Python scripts to addressing Configure, Build, Test and Package the project.

## Getting started
In order to spin up a fresh C++ development environment in your local repository just run the following command:

```bash
# Windows
env\setup.bat

# Linux / MacOS
./env/setup.sh
```